Class RBBEventListener.Adapter

Enclosing interface:
RBBEventListener
public static class RBBEventListener.Adapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements RBBEventListener

Here is a trivial implementation that routes event changes of any type to 'eventChanged', which also does nothing by default.

To ignore types of event changes you are not interested in, you can override the corresponding RBBEventListener method to do nothing.
